			   data-lightbox-sbi=""
			   data-title="Village salad - Greek Salad-ish but with no lettuce, chunky vegetables and a thick slab of feta. A thick slab of feta on anything is going to always win my vote. 😂 &lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
It’s easy and fast enough to make on Tuesday but impressive enough to serve to guests. It’s the classics like this that I’ll always make on repeat. &lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
Find the recipe on my website (link in bio) or comment RECIPE and I will send you the link. &lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
#villagesalad #greeksalad #saladrecipe #easydinners #bbqideas"
