			<a class="sbi_link_area nofancybox" rel="nofollow noopener" href="https://scontent-syd2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/732560533_18149478418503528_555466618083738434_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&#038;_nc_cat=111&#038;ccb=7-5&#038;_nc_sid=18de74&#038;efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&#038;_nc_ohc=Ui-I9ZYDV8cQ7kNvwEPnq6b&#038;_nc_oc=AdpK0Z5rG88oI6pqJq3vHGJvHgf2xf6Rb_O5leYdzI2q21s0PFzqLqlprbn2Fxf6Pw0&#038;_nc_zt=23&#038;_nc_ht=scontent-syd2-1.cdninstagram.com&#038;edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&#038;_nc_gid=K9RnyEUxnSaCPJOYU85rYQ&#038;_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQGOKLIQXyLzKONnK5AOk3KqmCdlZ_zAbvYfVtWtlW2ZEuURZNMHN2GYP20vhQtJOdbHnGm8EuL8MA&#038;oh=00_AQBFg8qOMrUr2joDO0myOxOCAGACKxI3KW0r-ICEU6sAkA&#038;oe=6A49C175"
			   data-lightbox-sbi=""
			   data-title="The biggest savings in our house rarely come from choosing the cheapest ingredients. They come from choosing dinners that actually make sense for real life.&lt;br&gt;
Recipes that use supermarket ingredients. Meals that don’t require buying three different sauces you’ll never use again. Dinners that make use of what you already have sitting in the fridge.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
Because when dinner feels complicated, expensive or overwhelming, that’s usually when takeaway starts looking very appealing. 😅&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
These are five dinners under $20 that my family loves. They’re simple, satisfying and realistic enough for busy weeknights when nobody has the energy for anything fancy.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
Here’s what’s on the menu:&lt;br&gt;
• Chicken Rissoles&lt;br&gt;
• Drunken Noodles&lt;br&gt;
• Stuffed Pita Arayes&lt;br&gt;
• Creamy Chicken Noodle Soup&lt;br&gt;
• Korean Beef Rice Bowls&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
Simple ingredients. Less food waste. Fewer specialty products. More dinners that actually get made.&lt;br&gt;
That’s the sweet spot for me. ❤️&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
Find the recipes on my website via the link in bio, or comment RECIPE and I’ll send you the links to all of these.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
#dinner #savingmoney #familydinner #easyrecipesathome👩🏻‍🍳❤️ #simpleingredients"
