Because when dinner feels complicated, expensive or overwhelming, that’s usually when takeaway starts looking very appealing. 😅

These are five dinners under $20 that my family loves. They’re simple, satisfying and realistic enough for busy weeknights when nobody has the energy for anything fancy.

Here’s what’s on the menu:
• Chicken Rissoles
• Drunken Noodles
