			<a class="sbi_link_area nofancybox" rel="nofollow noopener" href="https://scontent-syd2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/731754207_18149380621503528_6173262805634431223_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&#038;_nc_cat=108&#038;ccb=7-5&#038;_nc_sid=18de74&#038;efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0xJUFMuYmVzdF9pbWFnZV91cmxnZW4uQzMifQ%3D%3D&#038;_nc_ohc=FDd7ydy0QDAQ7kNvwH_dFcz&#038;_nc_oc=AdryayKAJQgHaRhjLFsFrzc5n2679GQylyWX7W38FNxgRVdtAN2mxgGjKLtGKX9I7Go&#038;_nc_zt=23&#038;_nc_ht=scontent-syd2-1.cdninstagram.com&#038;edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&#038;_nc_gid=K9RnyEUxnSaCPJOYU85rYQ&#038;_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQHMWRJPAekCenOwCyfgNnehgVGcko1N5hhbEiqj92nKQ7NhBYaII__zav5y6sA1qxXe6FRQ6AruDw&#038;oh=00_AQAwkMB88z-fgzoLGVa0EzPBdKnWXblXLH3W8E_yx7jlRQ&#038;oe=6A49AE9A"
			   data-lightbox-sbi=""
			   data-title="Southern “Fried” Baked Chicken Strips… without blowing up your entire kitchen with stove splatter and breadcrumbs everywhere. 😂&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
These are made in the oven and while there’s a fair bit happening here, it actually comes together really easily. I like making these on the weekend when I’m relaxed and need “fried-chicken-vibes” with my wine. 🤣&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
The sweet potato fries and chicken cook at the same time, it’s cheaper than takeaway and above all it feels a bit fun… and I think we all need dinners that remind us why we cook at home in the first place.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
Find the recipe on my website (link in bio) or comment RECIPE and I will send you the link.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
#weeknightdinner #crispychicken #fakeaway #familydinner #chickenrecipes #comfortfood #easydinners #simplehomeedit"
