These are made in the oven and while there’s a fair bit happening here, it actually comes together really easily. I like making these on the weekend when I’m relaxed and need “fried-chicken-vibes” with my wine. 🤣

The sweet potato fries and chicken cook at the same time, it’s cheaper than takeaway and above all it feels a bit fun… and I think we all need dinners that remind us why we cook at home in the first place.

Find the recipe on my website (link in bio) or comment RECIPE and I will send you the link.

